        <div class="container-fluid gray-block">
            <div class="container bd1-container">
                <h4 style="color: black;">Supports over 20 programming languages</h4>
                <div style="padding: 5px;">
                    <img src="c_lang_logo.png" height="50" style="margin: 20px;">
                    <img src="c++_lang_logo.png" height="50" style="margin: 20px;">
                    <img src="java_lang_logo.png" height="50" style="margin: 20px;">
                    <img src="python_lang_logo.png" height="50" style="margin: 20px;">
                    <img src="ruby_lang_logo.png" height="50" style="margin: 20px;">
                </div>
                <p class="scp">We use Judge0 API for code compilation that<br>supports a lot of programming languages.</p>
                <a class="btn btn-primary" id="lang-hide-btn">View all supported languages</a>
                <div class="lang-hide firstline">
                    <button class="btn btn-gray">Basic</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-gray">C#</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-gray">JavaScript</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-gray">Haskell</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-gray">Pascal</button>
                </div>
                <div class="lang-hide">
                    <button class="btn btn-gray">Rust</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-gray">OCaml</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-gray">Erlang</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-gray">Elixir</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-gray">Clojure</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bd1-container p3">
            <h4 style="color: black;">It's open source!</h4>
            <p class="scp">So check out the repository on GitHub if you<br>
                wanna upgrade your coding skill...</p>
            <a class="btn btn-cyan hoverblack" style="margin-top: 15px;" href="https://github.com/nisaruj/ngrader">I'm in!</a>
        </div>
